Provides an easy way to put your starling under daemontools supervise.

Setting the user for starling daemon:
    groupadd starling
    useradd -g starling -d /var/spool/starling -s /bin/false starling

daemontools: http://cr.yp.to/daemontools.html
Main project: http://rubyforge.org/projects/starling
